lead_paragraph: Madison Cable had 20 points and five steals Saturday to lead No. 2 Notre Dame to its third straight regular-season ACC title with a 70-58 win over Boston College.

headline.print_headline: No. 2 Notre Dame Tops Boston College Women 70-58
